,"location":2,"to":87.21},{"content":"像拐杖一样","from":87.45,"location":2,"to":88.29},{"content":"可以缓解肩膀酸痛的那种东西","from":88.29,"location":2,"to":89.74},{"content":"像痒痒挠一样的那种","from":89.74,"location":2,"to":90.76},{"content":"像这样用的话… 感觉能正好按到穴位","from":91.07,"location":2,"to":94.91},{"content":"不禁会让人拿来这么用","from":94.91,"location":2,"to":96.92},{"content":"的确会","from":96.92,"location":2,"to":97.45},{"content":"这到底是用来做什么的","from":97.45,"location":2,"to":98.48},{"content":"这个嘛… 各位认为是用来做什么的？","from":98.48,"location":2,"to":101.39},{"content":"猜谜了猜谜了","from":101.74,"location":2,"to":102.79},{"content":"我知道了我知道了","from":102.79,"location":2,"to":104.65},{"content":"最喜欢你了","from":105.82,"location":2,"to":106.47},{"content":"这…你把它拼成爱心了啊","from":107.15,"location":2,"to":108.63},{"content":"他笑了","from":109.42,"location":2,"to":110.16},{"content":"-角度也太刁钻了 -谢谢你的喜欢 -角度刁钻","from":110.28,"location":2,"to":112.3},{"content":"田中先生 最喜欢你了","from":112.84,"location":2,"to":114.5},{"content":"不是这么用的","from":115.58,"location":2,"to":116.11},{"content":"被直截了当地回绝了","from":117.49,"location":2,"to":118.69},{"content":"“不是这么用的”","from":118.91,"location":2,"to":119.66},{"content":"这也太难猜了","from":119.66,"location":2,"to":120.43},{"content":"我想到了 正经的","from":120.72,"location":2,"to":122.09},{"content":"是不是用来修齐底边弧线的","from":122.91,"location":2,"to":125.2},{"content":"是的 那个…这回答基本正确","from":125.52,"location":2,"to":128.47},{"content":"太强了","from":129.12,"location":2,"to":129.53},{"content":"像壶啊 花瓶啊","from":129.53,"location":2,"to":131.01},{"content":"做这种手够不着里面的作品就要拿着它伸进去…","from":131.52,"location":2,"to":136.36},{"content":"这么来调整形状","from":136.41,"location":2,"to":137.61},{"content":"是这么用的啊","from":137.62,"location":2,"to":138.97},{"content":"不是用手的啊","from":139.02,"location":2,"to":140.09},{"content":"接着令人在意的是这个工具","from":141.39,"location":2,"to":144.37},{"content":"这是…？","from":144.68,"location":2,"to":145.44},{"content":"上面写着“刨子”","from":146.52,"location":2,"to":147.93},{"content":"是的","from":147.93,"lo