","from":263.06,"location":2,"to":264.14},{"content":"我知道了！","from":265.05,"location":2,"to":265.72},{"content":"夹刚烧制出炉的盘子","from":266.14,"location":2,"to":267.52},{"content":"不对","from":267.96,"location":2,"to":268.51},{"content":"我和你想的一样","from":268.51,"location":2,"to":269.25},{"content":"我也是","from":269.25,"location":2,"to":269.91},{"content":"我也","from":269.91,"location":2,"to":270.31},{"content":"就是就是","from":270.31,"location":2,"to":271.18},{"content":"难道不就是嘛","from":271.39,"location":2,"to":272.12},{"content":"你们看看这里是卖什么的货架","from":272.12,"location":2,"to":273.35},{"content":"上色工具…？","from":273.75,"location":2,"to":274.81},{"content":"湿哒哒的！","from":274.81,"location":2,"to":275.55},{"content":"湿哒哒？","from":276.44,"location":2,"to":277.0},{"content":"湿淋淋的…","from":277.16,"location":2,"to":278.11},{"content":"原来是这么回事啊","from":279.29,"location":2,"to":280.35},{"content":"用来取还没干的东西","from":280.63,"location":2,"to":281.85},{"content":"对对","from":281.85,"location":2,"to":282.39},{"content":"取没干的东西吗","from":282.39,"location":2,"to":283.17},{"content":"…很可惜","from":283.45,"location":2,"to":284.19},{"content":"-答错了吗 -很可惜 -不对吗","from":284.4,"location":2,"to":286.29},{"content":"-是用它夹起盘子等等之后 -固定之后…","from":286.86,"location":2,"to":289.07},{"content":"一口气把它放进桶里","from":289.07,"location":2,"to":290.91},{"content":"还会有连着这个东西一起浸入釉药的大胆操作啊","from":291.5,"location":2,"to":294.03},{"content":"原来是这样啊","from":294.03,"location":2,"to":295.05},{"content":"-方法真是多变啊 -如果用手拿 那怎么都会留下指纹","from":295.05,"location":2,"to":298.43},{"content":"的确","from":298.43,"location":2,"to":299.05},{"content":"-这个施釉钳就是为了避免这种情况 -原来如此","from":299.05,"location":2,"to":302.94},{"content":"施釉钳啊","from":302.94,"location":2,"to":304.12},{"content":"全都是些我这辈子前所未见的东西","from":305.28,"location":2,"to":307.56},{"content":"要是不制作陶艺就基本不会接触到这些东西","from":307.98,"location":2,"to":309.84},{"content":"-就是啊 -是啊","from":309.84,"location":2,"to":310.82},{"content":"这里好有趣啊","from":310.96,"location":2,"to":312.08},{"content":"非常有